Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakra... Kam zmizela?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ach, tamhle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobře, jdeme!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel...
