Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,nevyšlo vniveč.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Starý pane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirojuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Roboti...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,mohou jít do nebe, že?
